Activities that will not raise your Trust Rank include: 
*Standing or idling in a room (AFKing).
*Uploading a large amount of low-effort content.
*Mass-friending large numbers of users.
*Harassment towards other VRChat users.
Additionally, subscribing to [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+|VRC+]], or being gifted a VRC+ subscription can increase your Trust Rank<ref>[https://hello.vrchat.com/vrchatplus VRC+] on VRChat's website; retrieved October 24, 2024.</ref>. However it will only increase it once.